Package com.example.freeturilo.core

Class RouteFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.freeturilo.core.RouteFragment
  • public class RouteFragment
extends java.lang.Object
    A bicycle route fragment.

    Object of this class represents a calculated NextBike bicycle route's fragment with its details. It encapsulates the cost, waypoints, parameters of calculation and the corresponding Google Maps route (directionsRoute) of the route fragment.

    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Miko≈Çaj Terzyk
